How to install Web server
1) login to aws accout with ec2-user
2) sudo su -
3) yum update -y
4) yum install httpd -y
5) service httpd start
6) cd /var/www/html and create index.html file with any content
eg <h1>Welcome to ec2</h1>

go to the browser and enter ec2 public ip address
		
	
	
	
	
	
	
